---
import LayoutV4 from '../../layouts/LayoutV4.astro';
---

<LayoutV4 title="Local Leader | Version 4 Scaffold">
  <main class="mx-auto flex min-h-screen w-full max-w-6xl flex-col justify-center px-6 py-20 sm:px-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500">Version 4</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-6xl">
        Version 4 is staged for the next <span class="font-serif italic">design direction</span>.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
        This scaffold gives the next planning and build agents a clean route, layout, and component directory to work
        from once the reference screenshots arrive.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-14 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Audience</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">
          Australian tradies who want stronger visibility, better leads, and more control over their pipeline.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Offer anchor</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">
          Become the #1 tradie in your area with stronger Maps rankings, page-one visibility, and better reviews.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Build status</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">
          Scaffold only. This page is intentionally lightweight so it can be replaced quickly during the build phase.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</LayoutV4>
